#: ../../source/user_guide/general/local_debug.rst:4
msgid "Local debug mode"
msgstr "本地调试模式"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/local_debug.rst:6
msgid ""
"This page introduces the features and usage of MaxFrame Local Debug Mode."
" Local Debug Mode allows you to debug UDF functions such as ``apply()`` "
"and ``apply_chunk()`` directly in your local environment, without "
"connecting to remote services."
msgstr ""
"本页介绍 MaxFrame Local Debug Mode 的能力和用法。Local Debug Mode 支持在"
"本地环境直接调试 ``apply()``、``apply_chunk()`` 等 UDF 函数，无需连接远程"
"服务。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/local_debug.rst:12
msgid "Background"
msgstr "背景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/local_debug.rst:13
msgid ""
"In the traditional MaxFrame UDF development workflow, debugging functions"
" such as ``apply()`` and ``apply_chunk()`` requires submitting code to a "
"remote cluster for execution. This makes it impossible to set breakpoints"
" or step through code locally. Every change has to be re-submitted for "
"remote execution, and you may have to maintain different code paths to "
"distinguish local development and production."
msgstr ""
"在传统的 MaxFrame UDF 开发流程中，调试 ``apply()``、``apply_chunk()`` 等"
"函数需要将代码提交到远程集群执行，因此无法在本地设置断点或单步调试。每次"
"修改后都需要重新提交远程执行，并且常常需要维护不同代码路径来区分本地开发"
"和生产运行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/local_debug.rst:20
msgid ""
"MaxFrame Local Debug Mode solves these problems. Once Local Debug Mode is"
" enabled, UDF functions are executed directly in the local Python "
"environment with full IDE breakpoint debugging support, work fully "
"offline, and the same code can be switched seamlessly between local "
"debugging and production runs."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame Local Debug Mode 用来解决这些问题。启用后，UDF 函数会直接在本地 "
"Python 环境中执行，完整支持 IDE 断点调试，可完全离线运行，并且同一份代码"
"可以在本地调试和生产执行之间无缝切换。"

